                        2. Poe Chatbot for Text-Based Business Tasks
                    </span>
                     <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transform transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
