                <div class="mt-4 text-slate-700 space-y-6 pt-4 border-t border-slate-200 pl-16 pr-3">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-800">2.1 What is Poe?</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2">Poe (<a href="https://poe.com" target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline font-semibold">poe.com</a>) is a platform where you can create a custom AI assistant by setting its instructions, personality, and example prompts.</p>
                        <p class="mt-2 font-semibold">Best for:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1 text-slate-600">
                            <li>Client Q&A</li>
                            <li>Proposal or report generation</li>
                            <li>Internal knowledge base</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-800">2.2 Step-by-Step Guide</h3>
                        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside mt-2 space-y-3 pl-4 text-slate-600">
                            <li><strong>Sign Up & Access Bot Builder:</strong> Go to <a href="https://poe.com" target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline font-semibold">poe.com</a>, sign up, and click "Create a bot."</li>
                            <li><strong>Choose a Base Model:</strong> Select Claude for detailed explanations or GPT-4o for short, clear answers.</li>
                            <li><strong>Write Bot Instructions:</strong> Clearly define the bot's role, audience, tone, and boundaries.</li>
                            <li><strong>Add a Welcome Message:</strong> Create a welcoming first message for users.</li>
                            <li><strong>Create Suggested Prompts:</strong> Provide clickable examples for users.</li>
                            <li><strong>Save & Test:</strong> Test with various queries to check tone, accuracy, and formatting.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div class="practice-box bg-slate-50 p-5 rounded-lg border-teal-500">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-800">Poe Self-Guided Practice</h3>
                        <div class="mt-3 space-y-3">
                            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Task: Create a Poe bot for a business of your choice.</p>
                            <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Write bot instructions (150–200 words).</label>
                            <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Add welcome message (1–2 sentences).</label>
                            <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Add 3 suggested prompts.</label>
                            <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Test and refine based on feedback.</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-5 space-y-3">
                             <p class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Self-Check Questions:</p>
                             <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Does the bot answer in a way that matches your brand tone?</label>
                             <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Does it know when to escalate to a human?</label>
                             <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Are its answers consistent when asked similar questions?</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-5 border-t border-slate-200 pt-4">
                             <label class="flex items-center font-bold text-teal-700 hover:text-teal-800 gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Mark Poe Chatbot Activity as Completed</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
