                <div class="mt-4 text-slate-700 space-y-6 pt-4 border-t border-slate-200 pl-16 pr-3">
                     <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-800">3.1 What is Meta AI Studio?</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2">Meta AI Studio lets you create AI characters for Messenger, Instagram, and WhatsApp.</p>
                        <p class="mt-2 font-semibold">Best for:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1 text-slate-600">
                            <li>Marketing interactions</li>
                            <li>Customer service on social channels</li>
                            <li>Lead qualification</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-800">3.2 Step-by-Step Guide</h3>
                        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside mt-2 space-y-3 pl-4 text-slate-600">
                            <li><strong>Access AI Studio:</strong> Visit <a href="https://ai.meta.com" target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline font-semibold">ai.meta.com</a>, log in, and click "Create AI."</li>
                            <li><strong>Name & Describe:</strong> Give your bot a clear name and description.</li>
                            <li><strong>Set Personality & Behavior:</strong> Define its style, do's, and don'ts.</li>
                            <li><strong>Add Welcome Message & Starters:</strong> Craft a greeting and provide example prompts.</li>
                            <li><strong>Enable Features:</strong> Enable search if needed and set public/private access.</li>
                            <li><strong>Publish & Test:</strong> Test for quick responses, clear options, and brand-safe language.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div class="practice-box bg-slate-50 p-5 rounded-lg border-sky-500">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-800">Meta AI Studio Self-Guided Practice</h3>
                        <div class="mt-3 space-y-3">
                            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Task: Build a social media bot for a business scenario.</p>
                            <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Define name, description, and personality.</label>
                            <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Add welcome message and 3 starter prompts.</label>
                            <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Test with a clear query, a vague request, and an off-topic question.</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-5 space-y-3">
                             <p class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Self-Check Questions:</p>
                             <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Does it engage naturally and encourage conversation?</label>
                             <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Does it avoid unsafe or off-brand responses?</label>
                             <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer"><input type="checkbox" class="custom-checkbox progress-checkbox">Is it easy for the user to continue chatting?</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-5 border-t border-slate-200 pt-4">
